So let's get started...'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 19, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be an image of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax In school, I was never the popular kid, I didn't have many friends and didn't really fit in. In fact, was getting severely bullied oullieo from 7th grade up until finishing high school. A few times it got to the point where we had to get the police involved.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 19, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be an image of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax Although school wasn't really an easy time for me, looking back, those times made me more independent and sparked my interest in business and personal development.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 19, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be an image of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax In high school, came across a social media marketing agency course. I realized could start that business because it didn't require a huge starting capital and could do it while was still at school. So I started my own agency.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 19, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be an image of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax In my last year of high school, started making $1-3K per month with my agency. It was nothing special but it was decent money at the time and it solidified that could eventually pursue my business full time.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 19, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax So in the final year of high school, had two options, either go to university or learn a trade. I never really saw myself pursuing either of those things and decided to start working full time on my marketing agency once I left school.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 19, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax I mostly got criticized for that but| didn't care and believed that made the right decision. So in September 2019 graduated from high schoo and my agency was making $1-3K at the time.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 19, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax By the end of 2019, scaled my agency to $20K per month. In 2020 $80K. had my record month of And in 2021 I've scaled my agency past $100K per month.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 19, 2021 tagging @itskaibax. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Kai Bax @itskaibax So that is the story of how I've built built my agency over the past 2 years. If you'd like to learn more about building a social media marketing agency, drop me a follow.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 18, 2021 tagging @richardgarciaofficial. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Richard Garcia @richardgarcia I'll admit, I was a bit lucky. I didn't have rich parents. My mom didn't didn't go to school. My dad passed away young. The only option had in life was to become successful because nobody around me was.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 18, 2021 tagging @richardgarciaofficial. May be a Twitter screenshot of 1 person and text that says 'Richard Garcia @richardgarcia Let me not get off track though. Here's a quick rundown of my corporate career. -Merrill Lynch in 2008 -Tesla in 2015 -Google in 2017 -Facebook in 2018 continued...'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 18, 2021 tagging @richardgarciaofficial. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Richard Garcia @richardgarcia When first started out in corporate @ Merrill Lynch, realized how EVERYONE was broke. Most of my peers would drive their BMW to work in Gucci Loafers and still be paycheck-to-paycheck paycheck-to While they're making $100k+ That's when to invest. realized that I needed'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 18, 2021 tagging @richardgarciaofficial. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Richard Garcia @richardgarcia Sol did... It sounds simple enough, but it took a lot of work. I saved and invested as much as possible (which wasn't easy because I hao a kid at 19). I ended going all-in on rea estate starting in 2011.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 18, 2021 tagging @richardgarciaofficial. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Richard Garcia @richardgarcia I bought three properties in 2011, and then the other five properties were purchased over the next nine years In total, my portfolio was worth ~$6.7M when I retired and it was composed of over 50 units.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 18, 2021 tagging @richardgarciaofficial. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Richard Garcia @richardgarcia I didn't invest crazy amounts into any of these either. I primarily used the BRRRR strategy and kept buying undervalued multifamily properties in Miami for dirt cheap. The cash flow from these properties alone allowed me to retire.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 18, 2021 tagging @richardgarciaofficial. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Richard Garcia @richardgarcia I knew could live comfortably off of $20,000/m. As of 2019, my properties were cash flowing about the same (net). That's when I knew I could retire.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 18, 2021 tagging @richardgarciaofficial. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Richard Garcia @richardgarcia I didn't nvest because it was the "cool thing to do" It took a lot of sacrifices, long weekends, and long nights to get to this point. But it's all all worth it because now I can do whatever want with my time.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 18, 2021 tagging @richardgarciaofficial. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Richaro Garcia @richardgarcia I'm here to share the lessons I've learned while building an $8M real estate portfolio. Not too many people have this much skin in the game on social media and you get to see my wins and losses in real-time. If you want to join me in my investing journey, follow me.'.

Photo shared by All About Making Money 💸 on September 18, 2021 tagging @basharjkatou. May be an image of 1 person, beard and text that says '-You wake up without an alarm -You are in no rush. -You plan out your day. -No traffic jams. -You work on your own terms. -You can take a break at any time. -Read or excercise when you want to. THAT'S FINANCIAL FREEDOM. @basharjkatou'.
